Azure pre-requisites
https://docs.openshift.com/container-platform/4.4/installing/installing_azure/installing-azure-account.html

Account limits to increase (will need to request via ticket, details in link above):
vCPU - 40
Public IP addresses - 3
Private IP addresses - 7

A domain registered and it's DNS configured with Azure:
https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/dns/dns-delegate-domain-azure-dns

Azure account must have following roles for subs:
User Access Administrator

https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/role-based-access-control/role-assignments-portal

A service principle created - details in doc above.
